QUICK START:

Install Wx::Perl::VirtualTreeCtrl by unpacking the tarball and running the following
commands in the source directory:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install
    Then delete the source directory tree since it's no longer needed.

    run 'perldoc Wx::Perl::VirtualTreeCtrl' to read the full documentation.
